{
  "stem": "4226.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 137,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was the first you head about it when you actually saw it happen.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 138,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 139,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, she carried the child.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 140,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She carried one.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 140,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And her friend, the doctor's wife, carried the other two children.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 141,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 142,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Both, both of them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 142,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they, they told, told us that in, in the weekend, the families will be reunited.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 143,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you believe it or you not.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 143,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] you couldn't do much.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 144,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father was with me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 145,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was-- he was sent with you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 146,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 147,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 148,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After next day, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I wrote a letter.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 148,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I got hold of a small pencil with one of the-- what you call them?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 148,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Outside of a tree.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 148,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 149,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The bark.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 149,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were some bits of white barks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 149,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were a particular tree that grow in Poland, in Russia, completely white bark.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 149,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You could peel it off and write on it like on paper.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 149,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I wrote a few words.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 149,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I throw it over to a camp which accommodated children who were at the age of 6-- between 6 and 15, girls and boys.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 149,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were even-- some were even praying with-- with [INAUDIBLE] in the morning.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 149,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The Germans kept them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 149,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Whenever a Swiss Red Cross comes to visit, they will show they have a special camp for the kids.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 149,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That camp was between, between our camp, which was called zigeunerlager, gypsy camp, because German gypsies were in charge of each barrack.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 149,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I ask that kid to throw it over to the next camp, where our women were.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 149,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And my auntie, who survived, she got that note from-- she told me after she got liberated, when we met.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
